data.description: Motivated Sellers they will consider all offers sent! Step into homeownership with this great starter home or possible rental property. Home has recently been painted, as well as new carpets in almost all the rooms. Garage has been converted into an additional bedroom, but can be converted back into a regular garage easily. Home needs a bit of TLC in some areas but has great potential for new homeowners or investors. Home is being sold as is.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from property owner.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
